## 🔄 Everything Connected:

```
StudentDB_Source.rds
        ↓ connects
StudentDataset (query runs)
        ↓ filtered by
Parameters (user input)
        ↓ displayed in
Table (user sees data) ✅

StudentList
        ↓ supplies values to
StudentName Parameter
        ↓ shows as
Dropdown in Preview ✅
```

